<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><a href="https://alferj.com/en/autori/anna-voltaggio/">Anna Voltaggio</a>, a Sicilian debut writer who now lives in Rome, works as a press officer in the cultural sector. <em>La nostalgia che avremo di noi</em> (Neri Pozza, 2023), the collection in which “Lucilla” appears, is her first publication.</p>
<div class="clear"></div>
<div class="imageleft">
