</div>
<p style="margin-bottom:16px"><strong><a href="https://amilanoappel.com/">Anne Milano Appel</a></strong> has translated texts by a number of leading Italian authors for US and UK publishers. Her shorter works have appeared in a variety of literary journals. Her awards include the Italian Prose in Translation Award, the John Florio Prize for Italian Translation, and the Northern California Book Award for Translation.</p>
